% Sample Queries:

% 1. Find all terrestrial planets
% ?- planet(Name, _, _, terrestrial).

% 2. Find the diameter of a planet
% ?- planet(earth, _, Diameter, _).

% 3. Find planets farther than 1000 million km from Sun
% ?- planet(Name, Distance, _, _), Distance > 1000.

% 4. Find all gas giants
% ?- planet(Name, _, _, gas_giant).

% 5. List all planets with their type
% ?- planet(Name, _, _, Type).
